Required programs:

soundtouch
lame
mplayer
youtube-dl (python lib), tested with version 2014.06.26
mediainfo
mpg123 (for flv videos)
faad2 (for mp4 videos)
elasticsearch

elasticsearch-analysis-morphology
installation (for elasticsearch 1.2.1):
$ sudo elasticsearch-plugin -install analysis-morphology -url http://dl.bintray.com/content/imotov/elasticsearch-plugins/org/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-analysis-morphology/1.2.0/elasticsearch-analysis-morphology-1.2.0.zip
